# NOTE: .terraform.lock.hcl is intentionally NOT gitignored.
# HashiCorp's official guidance is to commit the lock file so provider
# versions resolve identically across machines (your dev box, vendor
# environments, CI). It's the Terraform equivalent of package-lock.json.
# Pair this with plain `terraform init` (no -upgrade) in run.py so the
# lock isn't silently mutated on every workflow run.
